n\geq 1
\frac{1}{1^2}+\frac{1}{2^2}+\frac{1}{3^2}+\cdots+\frac{1}{n^2}\leq 2-\frac{1}{n}
2-\frac{1}{k}+\frac{1}{(k+1)^2} \leq 2-\frac{1}{k+1}
2-\frac{1}{k}+\frac{1}{(k+1)^2} \\ =2-\{\frac{1}{k}-\frac{1}{(k+1)^2}\} \\ =2-\{\frac{(k+1)^2-k}{k(k+1)^2}\}\\ =2-\{\frac{k^2+k+1}{k(k+1)^2}\}\\ \leq 2-\frac{k(k+1)}{k(k+1)^2}
k^2+k+1 \gt k^2+k\\ \frac{k^2+k+1}{k(k+1)^2} \gt \frac{k^2+k}{k(k+1)^2}\\  -\frac{k^2+k+1}{k(k+1)^2} \le -\frac{k^2+k}{k(k+1)^2}
